1
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:09,312
HAIDER: Alright, Iqrash, we got this. Hadi's been quiet lately, he's due for a hit.

2
00:00:09,312 --> 00:00:12,984
IQRASH: I don't know, man. Hadi's not one to back down from a fight.

3
00:00:12,984 --> 00:00:19,752
HAIDER: Don't worry, I've got a plan. We'll take him down, and then we'll be the top dogs in this city.

4
00:00:19,752 --> 00:00:21,168
IQRASH: What's the plan, again?

5
00:00:21,168 --> 00:00:26,592
HAIDER: We'll set up an ambush, and then we'll take him out. Easy as that.

6
00:00:26,592 --> 00:00:32,256
HAMMAD: Hey, guys, why don't you settle this like civilized people? In the annual car race, of course.

7
00:00:32,256 --> 00:00:38,266
HADI: Alright, baby, you're going to need to bring your A-game if we're going to take down Haider and Iqrash.

8
00:00:38,266 --> 00:00:44,866
HADI: This engine's been tweaked to perfection. I can feel it in my bones, we're going to win this thing.

9
00:00:44,866 --> 00:00:50,564
HAIDER: You think you can take me down, Hadi? I've been waiting for this moment for years.

10
00:00:50,564 --> 00:00:55,964
HADI: I'm not just looking to take you down, Haider. I'm looking to crush you.

11
00:00:55,964 --> 00:01:00,126
HADI: Come on, Haider! You can't keep up with me!

12
00:01:00,126 --> 00:01:02,886
HAIDER: I'm not going down without a fight!

13
00:01:02,886 --> 00:01:06,040
HAIDER: I...I didn't think you had it in you, Hadi.

14
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:12,040
HADI: You shouldn't have underestimated me, Haider. I'm the best driver in this city.
